libgpib_test is used by developers to test the library, feel free to add
tests for untested functions.  It requires two gpib boards to be installed
in the computer, on the same GPIB bus.  Exactly one of which is the system
controller.

Options:

-n, --num_loops N
	loop through tests N times
-d, --daemonize [N]
	daemonize after Nth loop


